    About me

    Who am I?

    Greetings,

    I am Kien, a recent graduate with a degree in Design (Digital Media) from RMIT University. Currently, I work as a UI/UX Designer at FPT Software, contributing to the largest design team in Southeast Asia, comprising over 140 talented designers. Additionally, I am pursuing an MBA at Western Sydney University.

    Beyond design, I find inspiration in my passion for music, particularly as a rapper and instrumentalist. These creative outlets not only enrich my personal life but also fuel the creativity I bring to my design work. You can check out my music on My Youtube

    Contact Me

    Experiences

    UI/UX Designer

    FPT Software

    Aug 2024 - Present

    Play a crucial role in the Bidding team, responsible for Ideation and Development of UI Design Concepts tailored specifically for large companies and corporations in fields such as Banking, Automotive, Retail and Shopping Center.

    Contribute to the UX Research process of Medical Pharmacy project by performing tasks such as creating comprehensive reports on competitor analysis, conducting market research, and participating in research user.

    Graphic Designer

    WESET English Center

    Jan 2022 - Apr 2022

    Craft social media posts for platforms including Facebook, Instagram, and the company website to enhance the brand s online presence.

    Contribute to designing the company catalog for a visually appealing representation of services.
